Yesterday I went to Tijuana with @thisisabouthumanity. First stop was their new relief kitchen, which, in partnership with @fundaciontijuanasinhambre @icfdn, provides over 2000 meals per day!

After that, we threw a holiday party for students at @YesWeCanWF, which is the first bilingual school program at the US-MX border providing migrant children full time education and safe spaces throughout their migrant journey. At Yes We Can, migrant children are cared for regardless of their legal status.

Thank you to our bus sponsor @scooterbraun for enabling this day to happen and to @angelakohler for the photos so that we are able to continue to spread awareness. @zoe.winkler.reinis @elsamariecollins 
#ThisisAboutHumanity
